are in chinese but will display the train service number which is printed at the top of your ticket). approx 10 minutes before boarding your train and platform will be announced and the gate will be opened, just follow the crowd to the platform - at larger stations the train will already be waiting, in smaller stations look for your car number written on the platform edge - make sure you're waiting in the right place because often the train will only stop for a couple of minutes. some newer stations have high-level platforms that are level with the door, 